---
// ReportPreview section
---

<!-- ── Report Preview ── -->
      <section class="section section--alt" id="report-preview">
        <div class="inner">
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="section__eyebrow">Le rapport généré</div>
            <h2>Ce que vous recevez<br /><em>en 2 minutes.</em></h2>
            <p class="section__lead">
              Pas un résumé vague. Chaque rendez-vous terrain génère un document complet en 11 sections — rédigé dans le vocabulaire de votre secteur, prêt à être envoyé ou archivé.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="report-preview-layout reveal">
            <div class="report-mock">
              <div class="report-mock__header">
                <div class="report-mock__meta">
                  <span class="report-mock__date">03 mars 2026 · 14h30</span>
                  <span class="report-mock__badge">Tourisme · Paris 8e</span>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__title">Agence Riviera — M. Laurent</div>
                <div class="report-mock__sub">Entretien de 48 min · Rapport généré en 1 min 42</div>
              </div>
              <div class="report-mock__body">
                <div class="report-mock__section report-mock__section--open">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">01</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Résumé exécutif</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="report-mock__section-content">
                    Agence active, 3e année de collaboration. Forte progression du segment MICE (+22% YoY). M. Laurent cherche à consolider l'allotement estival sur le produit Riviera Club. Opportunité de renouvellement contrat TO confirmée pour Q3.
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">02</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Profil &amp; contexte client</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">03</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Besoins exprimés</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">04</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Objections &amp; réponses</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">05</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Produits &amp; offres discutés</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">06</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Concurrents mentionnés</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">07</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Engagements mutuels</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">08</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Prochaines étapes &amp; échéances</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">09</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Opportunités identifiées</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">10</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Risques &amp; points de vigilance</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__section">
                  <div class="report-mock__section-head">
                    <span class="report-mock__section-num">11</span>
                    <span class="report-mock__section-title">Recommandations stratégiques</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="report-mock__footer">
                <div class="report-mock__footer-actions">
                  <div class="report-mock__action">
                    <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" stroke-width="1.8" style="width:14px;height:14px;stroke:var(--green)">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 10.5v2a1 1 0 001 1h8a1 1 0 001-1v-2M8 2v7m0 0L5.5 6.5M8 9l2.5-2.5"/>
                    </svg>
                    Export PDF
                  </div>
                  <div class="report-mock__action">
                    <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" stroke-width="1.8" style="width:14px;height:14px;stroke:var(--green)">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 8.5V13a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V3a1 1 0 011-1h4.5M10 2h4v4M14 2l-6 6"/>
                    </svg>
                    Partager
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="report-mock__privacy">
                  <svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 16 16" stroke-width="1.8" style="width:11px;height:11px;stroke:var(--muted);flex-shrink:0">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 1L2 4v4c0 3.31 2.69 6 6 7 3.31-1 6-3.69 6-7V4L8 1z"/>
                  </svg>
                  Audio supprimé après génération — privacy by design
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
